          "# 🎉 MulmoCast v1.0.12 Released!",
          "## March 3, 2026",
          "",
          "</div>"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "今回のアップデートでは、音声の読み上げ速度を細かく調整できるようになり、\n新しい画像生成モデルにも対応しました。",
      "id": "title-overview",
      "image": {
        "type": "beat",
        "id": "title-slide"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "1：TTS読み上げ速度オプションを追加しました。",
      "id": "speech-speed-intro",
      "image": {
        "type": "image",
        "source": {
          "kind": "path",
          "path": "images/01-01_speech_params_speed_openai.png"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "OpenAI TTSでは0.25倍速から4.0倍速まで読み上げ速度を調整できます。",
      "captionParams": {
        "captionSplit": "none",
        "textSplit": { "type": "none" }
      },
      "id": "speech-speed-openai",
      "image": {
        "type": "beat",
        "id": "speech-speed-intro"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "Google Cloud TTSでは0.25倍速から2.0倍速まで調整できます。",
      "captionParams": {
        "captionSplit": "none",
        "textSplit": { "type": "none" }
      },
      "id": "speech-speed-google-num",
      "image": {
        "type": "image",
        "source": {
          "kind": "path",
          "path": "images/01-02_speech_params_speed_google.png"
