      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "プロバイダーごとに設定可能な範囲が異なり、\nそれぞれの上限と下限がUIに表示されます。",
      "id": "speech-speed-google",
      "image": {
        "type": "beat",
        "id": "speech-speed-google-num"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "2：画像生成モデルにNano Banana 2を追加しました。\nGoogleの新しいモデル、",
      "id": "nano-banana-2-intro",
      "image": {
        "type": "image",
        "source": {
          "kind": "path",
          "path": "images/02-01_image_model_nano_banana.png"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "gemini-3.1-flash-image-previewが",
      "captionParams": {
        "captionSplit": "none",
        "textSplit": { "type": "none" }
