      "id": "nano-banana-2-model",
      "image": {
        "type": "beat",
        "id": "nano-banana-2-intro"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "画像モデル選択から利用可能です。",
      "id": "nano-banana-2",
      "image": {
        "type": "beat",
        "id": "nano-banana-2-intro"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Presenter",
      "text": "その他、軽微な改善を行いました。\n起動中のアプリに更新通知が届きます。\nダウンロードは公式サイトから行えます。",
      "id": "thank-you-slide",
      "image": {
        "type": "markdown",
        "markdown": [
          "<div style='display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; text-align: center;'>",
          "",
          "# Thank You!",
          "",
          "## MulmoCast v1.0.12",
          "",
          "### Happy Creating!",
          "</div>"
        ]
